Method: PATCH
ENDPOINT: /usermgt/v2/admin/users/{userIdentifier}

{userIdentifier} is the GUID of the current user. Use the GetIFSUserGUID_Tool to get this value before making an API call.

The following properties are available for updating: familyName givenName active userName defaultAccountingEntity title displayName preferredLanguage locale timezone ifsPersonId lnUser userAlias actorId federationId department manager.


Below is a valid request body for this API call. 
"op": "replace" should always be used.
"{property}": is to be replaced with the requested property from the user. valid properties are listed above.
"{Value}":  is to be replaced with the value provided by the user.

{
  "operations": [
    {
      "op": "replace",
      "path": "{Property}",
      "value": [
        {
          "value": "{Value}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
